00:43:47,360 --> 00:43:54,800
and other qualifying traumas. And we gave these individuals a trauma symptom checklist, a PTSD

427
00:43:54,800 --> 00:44:00,640
checklist. It's not the same as a diagnosis. This was done mainly during COVID, so it's done remotely,

428
00:44:00,640 --> 00:44:07,600
but it's a valid instrument to measure your symptoms of PTSD. And we found that 45% of

429
00:44:07,600 --> 00:44:14,240
