430
00:44:14,240 --> 00:44:19,920
percentage. In general population samples where they report having experienced a traumatic event

431
00:44:19,920 --> 00:44:27,760
like a physical assault, around 10% will go on to have persistent PTSD symptoms. So much, much

432
00:44:27,760 --> 00:44:33,840
higher percentage here for the autistic people. But the reason that I showed you a picture of a bus

